Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.90,0:01:49.42,Default,Tomomi:,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.68,0:01:50.25,Default,Girl:,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.74,0:01:52.46,Default,Boy:,0000,0000,0000,,That's bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.90,0:01:54.74,Default,Noda:,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, quit laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.12,0:01:56.56,Default,Noda:,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tomomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.12,0:01:57.62,Default,Tomomi:,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.24,0:02:03.74,Default,Tomomi:,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.84,0:02:14.04,Default,Noda:,0000,0000,0000,,I was sending telepathy.  Did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:16.01,Default,Tomomi:,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.01,0:02:18.96,Default,Boy:,0000,0000,0000,,So what did you tell her in telepathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.12,0:02:20.70,Default,Noda:,0000,0000,0000,,That I loved her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.70,0:02:21.54,Default,Tomomi:,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.54,0:02:22.74,Default,Noda:,0000,0000,0000,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.28,0:02:25.12,Default,Tomomi:,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.72,0:02:29.34,Default,Boy:,0000,0000,0000,,Noda, you really are an idiot, aren't ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.90,0:02:31.50,Default,Noda:,0000,0000,0000,,You finally noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.01,0:02:33.46,Default,Both:,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, we're just idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.20,0:02:48.46,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.80,0:03:00.07,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stupid Tomomi!  Why didn't she wake me up?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:01.94,Default,Cub:,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mom!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.64,0:03:34.44,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!  Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.70,0:03:55.56,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,That was really a close call, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.16,0:03:57.66,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.25,0:04:03.29,Default,Cub:,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mom...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.10,0:04:15.42,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just say mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.14,0:04:17.36,Default,Boy:,0000,0000,0000,,Heading your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.44,0:04:28.54,Default,Teacher:,0000,0000,0000,,There is a theory that until approximately 40 thousand years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.54,0:04:33.22,Default,Teacher:,0000,0000,0000,,humans communicated with animals though telepathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.56,0:04:35.12,Default,Daijuji:,0000,0000,0000,,Is that your theory?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:37.08,Default,Teacher:,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.34,0:04:41.56,Default,Daijuji:,0000,0000,0000,,Would you stop these silly talks and get back to the course material?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.84,0:05:09.39,Default,Tomomi:,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey Mikage.  Can't you at least knock first?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.69,0:05:11.10,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Knock.  knock.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.10,0:05:11.72,Default,Tomomi:,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.14,0:05:14.46,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Have you ever talked to animals using telepathy?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.01,0:05:16.94,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Have you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:19.84,Default,Tomomi:,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, I haven't.  Why?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.74,0:05:22.74,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Never mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.64,0:05:31.68,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,Kageura-sensei.  This is Mikage Matsunaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.18,0:05:33.66,Default,Teacher:,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:35.29,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:41.16,Default,Teacher:,0000,0000,0000,,Have you decided to participate in my experiment?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.04,0:05:45.08,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to ask you a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.92,0:05:48.34,Default,Teacher:,0000,0000,0000,,Now that's a rare event.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.58,0:05:52.14,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,Can humans really talk to animals using telepathy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.50,0:05:55.06,Default,Teacher:,0000,0000,0000,,Well?  Can you, Matsunaga?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.72,0:05:57.22,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,I asked you the question!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.98,0:06:04.45,Default,Teacher:,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.  I think you know far better than I do.  In the early days of history,
Comment: 0,0:06:08.60,0:06:11.94,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In the early days of human history,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.60,0:06:11.54,Default,Teacher:,0000,0000,0000,,It is believed that people used several means of communication.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.54,0:06:20.04,Default,Teacher:,0000,0000,0000,,Roughly speaking, they fall into three categories: audio/verbal, primitive
Comment: 0,0:06:12.88,0:06:14.06,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It is believed that people used several means of communication.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.04,0:06:25.07,Default,Teacher:,0000,0000,0000,,symbolic signs, and inter-mental communication, alias telepathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.07,0:06:30.91,Default,Teacher:,0000,0000,0000,,However, this ability degenerated as humans evolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:34.34,Default,Teacher:,0000,0000,0000,,Why?  It's because of all the tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.34,0:06:40.22,Default,Teacher:,0000,0000,0000,,The evolution of tools such as languages and letters led to the decline of telepathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.22,0:06:44.54,Default,Teacher:,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand, animals made a different choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.54,0:06:50.74,Default,Teacher:,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of using tools, the animals are using telepathy to communicate, I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:54.14,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,Then we can talk, can't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.37,0:07:04.74,Default,Teacher:,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, provided that you can use telepathy..like you two.
Comment: 0,0:06:57.42,0:07:18.08,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,telepathy to communicate, I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.54,0:07:06.94,Default,Bird:,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.54,0:07:12.05,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hello!  Hi!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.14,0:07:17.54,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hello?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.74,0:07:27.74,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, answer me.  Please?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:33.22,Default,Bird:,0000,0000,0000,,Good Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:36.84,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who was that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.84,0:07:38.08,Default,Bird:,0000,0000,0000,,Good Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.44,0:07:43.40,Default,Bird:,0000,0000,0000,,Good Morning.  Good Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.98,0:08:08.44,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come over.  Come here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.64,0:08:15.56,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.10,0:08:23.54,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,You stupid dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.14,0:08:37.98,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,You're the weird dog from this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.14,0:08:37.98,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did you find mom?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:40.99,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.56,0:08:45.16,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,I can't understand him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.08,0:08:53.66,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,It was just my imagination after all.\NIt's only Kageura's theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.74,0:08:56.68,Default,Cub:,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mom!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.29,0:09:13.32,Default,Tomomi:,0000,0000,0000,,So you brought this kitten home?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.56,0:09:16.44,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,Kitten?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.44,0:09:17.96,Default,Tomomi:,0000,0000,0000,,It's not?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.96,0:09:18.98,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,It's got to be a puppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.44,0:09:22.08,Default,Tomomi:,0000,0000,0000,,Puppy?  No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.66,0:09:30.84,Default,Tomomi:,0000,0000,0000,,You're a kitty, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.68,0:09:34.14,Default,Tomomi:,0000,0000,0000,,See?  It says it's a kitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:35.92,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,He told you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.70,0:09:38.76,Default,Tomomi:,0000,0000,0000,,No he didn't, but it's a cat alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.08,0:09:43.94,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,Bummer.  Didn't you say mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.14,0:09:53.82,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.70,0:10:01.01,Default,Tomomi:,0000,0000,0000,,Nice kitty.  Let's forget about that cold blooded woman over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.46,0:10:02.48,Default,Tomomi:,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:04.28,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,You pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.08,0:10:39.14,Default,Tomomi:,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should we do with him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.14,0:10:40.54,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're in charge.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.84,0:10:43.87,Default,Tomomi:,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What do you mean?  You brought him home.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.22,0:10:45.82,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sure I'm cold blooded.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.82,0:10:48.87,Default,Tomomi:,0000,0000,0000,,What a selfish bum.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.74,0:10:50.29,Default,Mom:,0000,0000,0000,,Who is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.86,0:10:51.52,Default,Tomomi:,0000,0000,0000,,Who's what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:53.01,Default,Mom:,0000,0000,0000,,Who is selfish?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.78,0:10:54.36,Default,Tomomi:,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.06,0:10:56.38,Default,Mom:,0000,0000,0000,,You said so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.76,0:10:57.60,Default,Tomomi:,0000,0000,0000,,Did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.87,0:11:01.25,Default,Mom:,0000,0000,0000,,Suddenly.  Strange Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:02.48,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,Really weird girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.14,0:11:07.52,Default,Mom:,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this in our neighborhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.34,0:11:14.54,Default,Newsman:,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H101360&}There's an update on the lioness and a cub that escaped from the circus.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.92,0:11:21.32,Default,Reporter:,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H101360&}A resident of the area reported seeing a lion.  The prefectual police is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.54,0:11:24.98,Default,Mom:,0000,0000,0000,,Well, better go to date with the lion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.48,0:11:26.98,Default,Tomomi:,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad you have to work on Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:28.94,Default,Mom:,0000,0000,0000,,It's not all that easy running a beauty parlor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.94,0:11:30.89,Default,Mom:,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you lock all the doors and windows.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.89,0:11:32.60,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.42,0:11:50.42,Default,Cub:,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mom.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.86,0:11:53.40,Default,Tomomi:,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.68,0:11:54.36,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,Did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:55.90,Default,Tomomi:,0000,0000,0000,,He said 'mom'.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.54,0:13:00.86,Default,Tomomi:,0000,0000,0000,,That's Right.  In the shopping district.\NYeah, that pet shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.86,0:13:03.24,Default,Tomomi:,0000,0000,0000,,It's safe around our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.24,0:13:07.82,Default,Tomomi:,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.  But the choppers from the TV stations are flying all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:10.34,Default,Tomomi:,0000,0000,0000,,What about your place Noda-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.34,0:13:13.34,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, say something other than mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.46,0:13:32.36,Default,Announcer:,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H101360&}The lion is heading north.\NMight be injured and dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.10,0:13:37.76,Default,Police:,0000,0000,0000,,Increase the patrol in the north half of the city.\NEnsure the safety of the citizens.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.16,0:13:51.70,Default,Cameraman:,0000,0000,0000,,There it is.  The lion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.92,0:13:52.86,Default,Reporter:,0000,0000,0000,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.70,0:14:03.52,Default,Reporter:,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it up.  We got her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.60,0:14:13.80,Default,Tomomi:,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, really?  Mikage, turn the TV on.\NThey're showing the lion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:15.20,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,The lion?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.19,0:14:22.52,Default,Reporter:,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H101360&}This is brought to you live.
