Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.29,0:14:33.14,Default,Reporter:,0000,0000,0000,,After her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:56.90,Default,Police:,0000,0000,0000,,Target sighted.  Will begin pursuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.52,0:15:05.48,Default,Police:,0000,0000,0000,,The target is heading east.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.94,0:15:16.08,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,So his mom was.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.54,0:15:19.56,Default,Tomomi:,0000,0000,0000,,He's a lion cub.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.46,0:15:22.01,Default,Noda:,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.08,0:15:31.36,Default,Reporter:,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you fly any lower?
