Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.74,0:15:33.74,Default,Reporter:,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.64,0:16:44.38,Default,Cub:,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mom!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.59,0:17:12.22,Default,Police:,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper One to headquarters.  We have sealed off the area completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.74,0:17:14.22,Default,Police:,0000,0000,0000,,Will begin capture of the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:15.68,Default,Police:,0000,0000,0000,,Headquarters, roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.70,0:17:21.22,Default,Reporter:,0000,0000,0000,,This is the park where the lion is.\NIt is now completely sealed off.
Comment: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:23.94,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It is now completely sealed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:24.25,Default,Reporter:,0000,0000,0000,,With the presence of all the media, the area is quite chaotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.25,0:17:26.74,Default,Reporter:,0000,0000,0000,,According to the police briefing, they plan to use tranquilizers,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.74,0:17:29.74,Default,Reporter:,0000,0000,0000,,but they will have riflemen ready just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.14,0:17:45.68,Default,Tomomi:,0000,0000,0000,,Are you OK, Mikage?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.18,0:19:08.20,Default,Police:,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, watch out!  Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.72,0:19:31.38,Default,Tomomi:,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.50,0:19:33.76,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.01,0:20:09.08,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,I bet they wanted to go back to Africa...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:10.76,Default,Tomomi:,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.01,0:20:18.29,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,But they probably wouldn't have survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.99,0:20:21.06,Default,Tomomi:,0000,0000,0000,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.60,0:20:28.01,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause they've been captive for so long that they probably forgot how to find food.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:30.78,Default,Tomomi:,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.58,0:20:33.12,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi, don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.50,0:20:35.87,Default,Tomomi:,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:37.60,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,I said cut it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.24,0:20:39.86,Default,Tomomi:,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.34,0:20:44.04,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:46.24,Default,Tomomi:,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.06,0:21:09.50,Default,Mikage:,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.29,0:21:19.29,Default,Tomomi:,0000,0000,0000,,Mom must be worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.06,0:21:52.32,Default,Tomomi?:,0000,0000,0000,,Miracle Girls here.\NYahoo!  We're off for skiing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.64,0:21:54.38,Default,Tomomi?:,0000,0000,0000,,I heard there's going to be a storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.86,0:21:56.39,Default,Tomomi?:,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi, we'll be stranded.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.39,0:21:57.25,Default,Tomomi?:,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.94,0:22:00.92,Default,Tomomi:,0000,0000,0000,,Next on Miracle Girls, "Snowstorm in Lodge"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.70,0:22:03.86,Default,Girs:,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that the snowman lives there?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.80,0:22:12.32,notes,note,0000,0000,0046,,{\a6}Original air date Feb. 26, 1993.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.91,0:22:07.99,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever we do,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.43,0:22:11.48,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,there has to be both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.35,0:22:18.20,credits,Credit,0000,0000,0046,,{\a7}Matsunaga Tomomi ...Fujieda Nariko\NMatsunaga Mikage........Nagai Noriko
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.56,0:22:14.60,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we had a fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.03,0:22:18.13,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,there has to be both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.23,0:22:24.74,credits,Credit,0000,0000,0046,,{\a5}Noda Yuhya...........Yamaguchi Kappei\NKurashige Hideaki...Shiozawa Kaneto
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.77,0:22:31.75,notes,note,0000,0000,0046,,{\a6}Miracle Girls on internet http://www.tcp.com/doi/miracle/miracle.html
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.97,0:22:38.12,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,There are days when kindness is so close that you can't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.77,0:22:38.17,notes,note,0000,0000,0046,,{\a6}Miracle Girls Original Soundtrack Sony Records SRCL 2574
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.20,0:22:45.69,credits,Credit,0000,0000,0046,,{\a7}Shinichiroh Kageura...Ken Yamaguchi\NDaijohji Rumiko.................Sakuma Rei
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.48,0:22:50.01,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we know better than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.72,0:22:52.03,credits,Credit,0000,0000,0046,,{\a5}Yamagishi Kouhei.......Nobuh Tobita
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.06,0:22:58.50,creditfansub,Credit,0000,0000,0046,,{\a6}Timed and Edited by Fred Werth.\NTyped by Brent Wallace.\NProofed by Tina Barrie.\NAdditional editing by Miwa.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.33,0:22:58.12,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,When we can't say "I'm sorry,"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.54,0:23:03.24,creditfansub,Credit,0000,0000,0046,,{\a7}Subtitled by Studio Hooseki\Nwww.miwasoft.com/hooseki
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.23,0:23:05.70,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,we send out feelings through the little fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.83,0:23:11.30,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,Going over the tears,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.10,0:23:14.68,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,we want to be honest to ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.10,0:23:20.47,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause the sky deserves a rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.86,0:23:22.98,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever we do,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.34,0:23:26.55,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,there has to be both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.50,0:23:29.68,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,Two of us
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.99,0:23:33.85,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,are better than one of us.
